snippet.title: [c64] Andy Capp (1987)
snippet.description:
I made some cuts in the video to reduce repetition and also to make my playing look more sober than it actually was.

This is somewhat similar to Garfield, Ghettoblaster and Jack the Nipper.

Music by Jason C. Brooke, Published by Mirrorsoft

http://www.lemon64.com/games/details.php?ID=112
